Therefore, we can conclude that:

\begin{align*}
\mathbb{P}\left(\frac{1}{n}\sum_{j=1}^{n}X_j \geq 2\right) \leq \frac{1}{B} \leq \sum_{m=1}^{\infty} f(m) < A.
